# 3. Containerfile (41 Lines)

Stage 1 (FROM scratch AS ctx): Copies scripts/, PACKAGES.md, VERSION, system_files/ into scratch for bind-mount. Stage 2 (FROM quay.io/fedora/fedora-bootc:rawhide): Single RUN sets SYSTEMD_OFFLINE=1 + container=podman (prevent scriptlet hangs), creates writable /tmp/build, copies from read-only bind mount, strips CRLF via sed, makes .sh executable, runs build.sh, removes /tmp/build. Second RUN copies system_files/ overlay into root + dconf update. Labels containers.bootc=1 and ostree.bootable=1. Final bootc container lint validates.

Critical constraint: bind mounts from ctx are READ-ONLY. Any sed -i or chmod must operate on /tmp/build copies.

# 4. cloud-ws.ps1 — Windows Orchestrator (325 Lines)

Phase 0 (Lines 76-98): Timed prompts for username, password, LUKS, registry. Reads MIOS_GHCR_USER/TOKEN env vars. Validates Podman, CPU, RAM, required files.

Phase 1 (Lines 115-134): Creates dedicated mios-builder Podman machine (--rootful, all cores, all RAM, 250GB disk). Never touches default machine.

Phase 2 (Lines 136-170): Replaces INJ_U/INJ_P in 99-overrides.sh, runs podman build --no-cache, immediately restores placeholders via git checkout. Rechunks via bootc-base-imagectl for 5-10x smaller Day-2 updates.

Phase 3 (Lines 172-261): BIB targets: RAW (--type raw, ext4, 80GiB via /config.json), VHD-to-VHDX (qemu-img convert in Alpine container), WSL (podman create+export), ISO (--type anaconda-iso). Each target cleans intermediates.

Phase 4 (Lines 263-287): podman login + push to GHCR. Auto-sets package public via GitHub API PATCH. Phase 5 (Lines 289-326): Restores default Podman machine, stops builder, prints 5-target report with sizes and deploy commands.

# 5. PACKAGES.md (472 Lines)

Single source of truth for all packages. 19 fenced code blocks: packages-repos (4), packages-kernel (10), packages-gnome (65), packages-gnome-core-apps (~18, all commented), packages-gpu-mesa (8), packages-gpu-amd-compute (2), packages-gpu-nvidia (3), packages-virt (11), packages-containers (14), packages-cockpit (12), packages-wintools (5), packages-security (8), packages-gaming (14), packages-guests (6), packages-storage (17), packages-ha (17), packages-utils (18), packages-android (1), packages-looking-glass-build (20), packages-cockpit-plugins-build (2). Total ~240 explicit RPMs + 5 Flatpaks.

Design: comments (#) inside blocks are skipped by sed parser. gnome-core-apps section is entirely commented — users uncomment to enable. install_packages_optional() detects this and logs appropriately. All user-facing apps are Flatpaks (uninstallable). Only system-level apps (Steam, Wine, virt-manager, Waydroid) are RPMs.

# 6. scripts/build.sh (102 Lines)

Master runner invoked from Containerfile. Tees output to /tmp/mios-build.log. Validates PACKAGES.md. Sets DNF tweaks (install_weak_deps=True, SYSTEMD_OFFLINE=1). Iterates [0-9][0-9]-*.sh in glob order, timing each. Failures logged but don’t abort (set -e within scripts, not between). Final cleanup: dnf clean all, rm caches, copy log to /var/log/mios-build.log, rm /tmp/*.

# 7. scripts/lib/packages.sh (81 Lines)

get_packages(): sed extracts between fenced markers, strips blanks/comments, joins with spaces. install_packages(): wraps dnf -y install --skip-unavailable. install_packages_strict(): fails on empty result. install_packages_optional(): distinguishes all-commented (intentional disable) from missing section vs uncommented packages.

# 8–13. Numbered Build Scripts

Installs RPMFusion Free+Nonfree from direct Rawhide URLs. Uses URL install rather than packages-repos section because repos must exist before other packages resolve.

install_packages_strict kernel. Captures KVER = highest kernel in /lib/modules for akmod builds.

Individual GNOME packages (NOT @gnome-desktop group). Optional core apps via install_packages_optional. Enables GDM+NetworkManager, graphical.target. Installs Geist font (GitHub clone), Bibata cursor (v2.1.0 tarball). Adds Flathub, Flathub Beta, GNOME Nightly remotes. Pre-installs Epiphany+Logs (gnome-nightly first for LibAdwaita match, Flathub fallback), Extension Manager, Podman Desktop, VSCodium. Flatpak theming: filesystem overrides for GTK config dirs, ADW_DEBUG_COLOR_SCHEME=prefer-dark (NOT GTK_THEME which breaks libadwaita).

Three-tier GPU: Mesa strict (Vulkan/DRI/VA + firmware + microcode), ROCm fault-tolerant, NVIDIA akmod with forced kmod build + CDI spec generation.

Mega-installer. 11 package categories + 5 manual installs. CrowdSec with Fedora 40 fallback repo + sovereign config. K3s binary + symlinks. xRDP vsock for Hyper-V Enhanced Session. Cockpit plugins from git. VirtIO-Win ISO download. Looking Glass B7 compile from source then build-dep removal.

Enables core services (libvirtd, cockpit, tuned, PCP, firewalld, chronyd). Optional services fail-silent (CrowdSec, fapolicyd, USBGuard, guests, Samba/NFS, Tailscale, xRDP, Waydroid, cloud-init, Podman). TuneD throughput-performance.

# 14. scripts/99-overrides.sh (621 Lines)

17 configuration sections:

| **Section** | **Implementation** |
| --- | --- |
| §0 PAM | authselect select local --force + manual pam_unix fallback if authselect fails |
| §1 User | useradd -m -d /var/home/INJ_U, chpasswd for user+root, passwd -u unlock |
| §2 Groups | sed injection into /etc/group for wheel/libvirt/kvm/video/render/input/dialout |
| §3 Sudoers | %wheel NOPASSWD via /etc/sudoers.d/wheel |
| §4 CLI | mios() help function, scan-malware alias (containerized ClamAV), fastfetch on terminal open |
| §5 Locale | en_US.UTF-8 via locale.conf + localedef |
| §6 Hostname | MiOS-<machine-id-6char> for HA uniqueness + systemd service |
| §7 Cloud-init | preserve_hostname, ssh_pwauth, default_user, multi-cloud datasource list |
| §8 Multipath | user_friendly_names, find_multipaths |
| §9 Firewall | Guard (checks firewalld active), drop zone default, opens cockpit/ssh/rdp/samba/nfs/k3s/pcs, trusts lo/podman0/virbr0/cni0/flannel.1/waydroid0 |
| §10 GPU Detect | systemd service before GDM: VMs get NVIDIA blocked + Cairo renderer, bare metal gets hardware renderer |
| §11 Init Service | Every boot: hostname, home dirs, groups, firewall, CrowdSec registration, PCP, Flatpak dark theme, Hyper-V enhanced session, bootc status |
| §12 Tools | 14 scripts: mios-update/build/rebuild/backup/deploy/vfio-toggle/hostname + iommu-groups + Cockpit .desktop |
| §13 Bloat | NoDisplay=true for 27 .desktop entries (gnome-tour, malcontent, Wine utils, nvidia-settings, etc.) |
| §14 NFS | mkdir /var/lib/nfs/statd + tmpfiles.d rule |
| §15 VM Mask | ConditionVirtualization=yes service: WSL2 masks gdm/firewalld/waydroid/nvidia/crowdsec, KVM/VMware masks nvidia/crowdsec-bouncer |
| §16 SELinux | restorecon, semanage fcontext, setsebool for dump_core/mmap_files/virt_sandbox/virt_use_nfs |
| §17 Autostart | First-login .desktop installs Bottles from flathub-beta then self-deletes |

# 15. System Configuration Overlays (19 Files)

Dark mode via color-scheme=prefer-dark, Geist 11pt, Bibata cursor, Dash-to-Dock bottom/48px, 5 app folders, favorites, AppIndicator+DtD extensions.

ADW_DEBUG_COLOR_SCHEME=prefer-dark (NOT GTK_THEME), Qt adwaita-dark, Electron Ozone, MOZ_ENABLE_WAYLAND, SDL_VIDEODRIVER=wayland,x11, ENABLE_HDR_WSI.

modeset=1 (Wayland DRM), fbdev=1 (early boot), EnableGpuFirmware=1 (GSP), PreserveVideoMemoryAllocations=1 (suspend/resume VRAM).

ntsync (Wine/Proton game compat), vfio-pci (early for driverctl), hv_sock (Hyper-V Enhanced Session).

swappiness=10, overcommit=1, dirty_ratio=20/5, ip_forward=1, bridge-nf-call=1, inotify 1M/8K.

root-fs-type=xfs for bare-metal. zram-generator: min(RAM/2, 32G) zstd. K3s unit: Type=notify, unlimited resources, auto-restart.

# 16. Key Engineering Principles

| **Principle** | **Detail** |
| --- | --- |
| Immutability-first | Everything baked at build time. Zero post-install pulls. Air-gapped deployable. |
| Bind mounts read-only | Copy to /tmp/build before sed -i or chmod. |
| PACKAGES.md single source | No package lists duplicated. sed parser. One file to edit. |
| INJ_U/INJ_P injection | Orchestrator string-replaces, git checkout restores immediately. |
| Hardware-agnostic image | GPU auto-detect: blocks NVIDIA in VMs, enables virtual GPU, forces Cairo renderer. |
| NoDisplay over dnf remove | malcontent removal cascades to gnome-shell. Hide with NoDisplay=true instead. |
| authselect local --force | pam_lastlog.so removed in Fedora 43+. Local profile with zero features only reliable path. |
| /var/home not /home | bootc symlinks /home to /var/home. User home = /var/home/<user>. |
| ADW_DEBUG_COLOR_SCHEME | NOT GTK_THEME. GTK_THEME forces legacy GTK3 chrome on libadwaita apps. |
| Firewall guard | Checks firewall-cmd exists AND firewalld active. WSL2/containers lack nftables. |
| Dynamic HA hostname | MiOS-<machine-id-6char> ensures unique hostnames from identical images. |
| SYSTEMD_OFFLINE=1 | Prevents %post scriptlets from starting services in container builds (hangs). |
| BIB mount path matters | Parser selected by extension: /config.json=JSON, /config.toml=TOML. Wrong extension = silent failure. |
| .gitattributes LF | All text LF. Only .ps1/.bat CRLF. CRLF in .sh = bad interpreter in containers. |
| push-to-github.ps1 overwrites | Flat files always replace existing. Prevents stale cached copies. |
| CrowdSec F40 fallback | Rawhide may lack packages. Auto-adds Fedora 40 baseurl repo. |